<L>__{exterior city park. day.}
<A>__{truman eats lunch alone on a concrete bench in a cement park. from his briefcase he pulls out an old hardcovered book, "to the ends of the earth the age of exploration". a transient in a wheelchair approaches, looking for a handout. truman gives the homeless man half of his sandwich, reconsiders and gives him it all, his appetite gone. as the transient wheels himself away, truman loses himself in his book.}
